            "title": "美圖歸母淨利跌近13%  自股份溢價賬派末期息  今復牌",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">美圖公司(01357)公布2025年度業績，歸屬母公司權益持有人淨利潤6.98億元，按年跌12.7%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">公司公布，自股份溢價賬派付末期股息，每股0.05元。連中期0.045元，全年派0.095元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：美圖官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230718-103142_source-web_01357美圖-7_source-web_.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：美圖官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230718-103142_source-web_01357美圖-7_source-web_.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：美圖官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">經調整歸屬母公司權益持有人淨利潤9.65億元，按年升64.7%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">收入38.59億元，按年升28.8%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">公司今天上午9時恢復買賣。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15810435-%e7%be%8e%e5%9c%96%e6%ad%b8%e6%af%8d%e6%b7%a8%e5%88%a9%e8%b7%8c%e8%bf%9113-%e8%87%aa%e8%82%a1%e4%bb%bd%e6%ba%a2%e5%83%b9%e8%b3%ac%e6%b4%be%e6%9c%ab%e6%9c%9f%e6%81%af-%e4%bb%8a%e5%be%a9%e7%89%8c",
