        {
            "title": "招行去年純利按年升1.21% 淨利差降0.08個百分點 擬派末期息每股1.003元人幣",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">招商銀行(03968)公布，在2025年度歸屬銀行股東淨利潤1501.81億元(人民幣．下同)，按年升1.21%；擬派末期息每股1.003元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：招商銀行官網影片截圖\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/09/bplib_20230718-143159_source-web_03968.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：招商銀行官網影片截圖\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/09/bplib_20230718-143159_source-web_03968.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：招商銀行官網影片截圖</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">計入已派中期息每股1.013元，全年每股共派2.016元，較2024年度的2元微增0.8%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">期內招行營業淨收入3372.73億元，按年微升0.05。稅前利潤1789.93億元，增長0.19%。淨利差1.78%，按年下降0.08個百分點；淨利息收益率1.87%，按年減少0.11個百分點。淨利息收入佔營業淨收入比例63.92%，按年升1.25個百分點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">至於去年的不良貸款率，則降至0.94%，按年減0.01個百分點；撥備覆蓋率391.79%，按年降20.19個百分點；貸款撥備率3.68%，按年降0.24個百分點。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">一級資本充足率16.51%，按年下降0.97個百分點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15810361-%e6%8b%9b%e8%a1%8c%e5%8e%bb%e5%b9%b4%e7%b4%94%e5%88%a9%e6%8c%89%e5%b9%b4%e5%8d%871-21-%e6%b7%a8%e5%88%a9%e5%b7%ae%e9%99%8d0-08%e5%80%8b%e7%99%be%e5%88%86%e9%bb%9e-%e6%93%ac%e6%b4%be%e6%9c%ab%e6%9c%9f",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/09/20240902_FI_source-web_03968.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-30 09:06:31",
